text: Dumortier is a surname of French origin. People with that name include: * André Dumortier (1910-2004), Belgian pianist * Augustin Dumon-Dumortier (1791-1852), Belgian industrialist, diplomat and liberal politician * Barthélemy Charles Joseph Dumortier (1797-1878), Belgian botanist and Member of Parliament (standard botanical abbreviation Dumortier) * Eugène Dumortier (1802-1876), French paleontologist * François-Xavier Dumortier (born 1948), French Roman Catholic priest ==See also== * Category:Surnames of French origin
